starvationevasion.common.messages

Class AvailableRegions

  • java.lang.Object
    • starvationevasion.common.messages.AvailableRegions

  • public class AvailableRegions
extends java.lang.Object
    Shea Polansky A listing of which regions are available, and which are taken. An instance of this message will be transmitted at least, but possibly more than, once every time a player changes their chosen region.
